title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 27 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 27 2022
description:
New York Post Twitter account hacked with absurd headlines, Hochul staff believes it. Elon Musk takes over Twitter, should Trump go back? Pennsylvania says election results will take days. Dr. Scott Jensen joins Clay and Buck, as he aims to take down Minnesota Governor Walz. NBC News story quotes numerous Democrats admitting the truth about the Fetterman debate.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
